===Etymology===
From the [[Low Greek]] ''mithraikos'', from the [[Greek]] ''Mithras'', from the [[Old Persian]] ''Mithra.'' It was admitted into English ca. 1678.
===Adjective===
Of or relating to the Asian mystery [[cult]] that existed the in the late [[w: Roman Empire]].

